	(16550, 2, 0, 'Judging by your signal, we put you... ust southeast of the larger part of the island we crashed onto.  Cross the Crystalbrook River to ge... kshhhhk zzzt. Sorry, there\'s a lot of stat...', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 12753, 0, 'Image of Technician Dyvuun'),
