	(16590, 0, 0, 'If my stomach wasn\'t threatening to dislodge itself from my body and leave me for the refuse that we give to the prisoners, I might be insulted by this... this food.', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 12550, 0, 'Injured Thrallmar Grunt'),
