	(19701, 0, 2, 'Your bones will be devoured!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 12839, 0, 'Bonechewer Evoker'),
	(19701, 0, 3, 'Protect the Warchief at all costs!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 12836, 0, 'Bonechewer Evoker'),
	(19710, 0, 0, 'You have approximately five seconds to live.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11109, 0, 20033, 0, 'ironhand SAY_AGGRO_1'),
	(19710, 1, 0, 'With the precise angle and velocity...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11112, 0, 18662, 0, 'ironhand SAY_HAMMER_1'),
	(19710, 1, 1, 'Low-tech, yet quite effective.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11113, 0, 20029, 0, 'ironhand SAY_HAMMER_2'),
	(19710, 2, 0, 'A foregone conclusion.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11110, 0, 20031, 0, 'ironhand SAY_SLAY_1'),
	(19710, 2, 1, 'The processing will continue as scheduled!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11111, 0, 20032, 0, 'ironhand SAY_SLAY_2'),
	(19710, 3, 0, 'My calculations did not...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11114, 0, 20030, 0, 'ironhand SAY_DEATH_1'),
	(19710, 4, 0, '%s raises his hammer menacingly...', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20710, 0, 'ironhand EMOTE_HAMMER'),
	(19720, 0, 0, 'Time to teach you a lesson in manners, little $g boy:girl;!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17353, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19720, 1, 0, 'Now I\'m gonna give you to the count of \'3\' to get out of here before I sick the dogs on you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17354, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19720, 2, 0, '1...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29261, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19720, 3, 0, '2...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29260, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19720, 4, 0, 'Time to meet your maker!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17357, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19720, 5, 0, 'Alright, we give up! Don\'t hurt us!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17361, 0, '"Dirty" Larry'),
	(19737, 0, 0, 'The ship\'s not ready yet.  We still need to calibrate the fuse length to make sure that it doesn\'t burn out and leave you up there alone.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17414, 0, 'Engineering Crewmember'),
	(19737, 1, 0, 'Essentially, it\'s going to be a long, long time till we are ready to launch.  Maybe you should just head back home to your family.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17417, 0, 'Engineering Crewmember'),
	(19737, 2, 0, 'Why not? A family can give you strength.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17420, 0, 'Engineering Crewmember'),
	(19737, 3, 0, 'Couldn\'t you raise them?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17422, 0, 'Engineering Crewmember'),
	(19737, 4, 0, 'Well, it\'s like I said; it\'s going to be a while before we get this ship ready for flight.  We\'ll keep you informed.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17424, 0, 'Engineering Crewmember'),
	(19747, 0, 0, 'Make ready the chambers, another ally will soon join our ranks!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19416, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 1, 0, 'Our ally has arrived!  Clear the way to the materialization chamber!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19417, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 2, 0, 'Now, proceed to the translocator. Forge Camp Wrath awaits your arrival!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19418, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 0, 'Prepare yourself for eternal torture, mortal!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20366, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 1, 'WHAT?! Who dares to disturb the Burning Legion?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20365, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 2, 'I shall enjoy the smell of the grease from your marrow crackling over the fire!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20368, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 3, 'Nothing will prevent your doom!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20367, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 4, 'You DARE to attack me?!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20369, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 3, 5, 'You will suffer slowly until the end of time for this affront!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20370, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19747, 4, 0, 'Release the hounds!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20395, 0, 'Baelmon the Hound-Master'),
	(19763, 0, 0, 'Thank goodness you got here, it was almost dinner time!', 12, 0, 100, 3, 0, 0, 0, 17407, 0, 'Manni'),
	(19764, 0, 0, 'I thought I was a goner for sure.', 12, 0, 100, 4, 0, 0, 0, 17409, 0, 'Moh'),
	(19766, 0, 0, 'I don\'t know which is worse, getting eaten by fel orcs or working for that slave master Razelcraz! Oh well, thanks anyways!', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 0, 0, 17410, 0, 'Jakk'),
	(19776, 0, 0, 'All my bags are packed, I\'m ready to go.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17413, 0, 'Experimental Pilot'),
	(19776, 1, 0, 'You need to do what? All this science, I don\'t understand... Look, this is just my job, five days a week.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17416, 0, 'Experimental Pilot'),
	(19776, 2, 0, 'I can\'t. I\'m not the man they think I am at home.  Besides, I didn\'t bring them out here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17419, 0, 'Experimental Pilot'),
	(19776, 3, 0, 'This isn\'t the kind of place to raise your kids. It\'s cold, and there\'d be no one to raise them.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17421, 0, 'Experimental Pilot'),
	(19776, 4, 0, 'Oh no, no, no... I\'m a rocket man.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17423, 0, 'Experimental Pilot'),
	(19827, 0, 0, '%s becomes enraged!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 24144, 0, 'Dark Conclave Ravenguard'),
	(19830, 0, 0, 'You cannot be serious!  We are severely understaffed and can barely keep this manaforge functional!', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 18166, 0, 'dawnforge SAY_ARCANIST_ARDONIS_1'),
	(19830, 1, 0, 'Yes, my lord.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 19189, 0, 'dawnforge SAY_ARCANIST_ARDONIS_2'),
	(19831, 0, 0, 'We need you to send reinforcements to Manaforge Duro, Ardonis.  This is not a request, it\'s an order.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 18165, 0, 'dawnforge SAY_COMMANDER_DAWNFORGE_1'),
	(19831, 1, 0, 'You will do as ordered.  Manaforge Duro has come under heavy attack by mana creatures and the situation is out of control.  Failure to comply will not be tolerated!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 18167, 0, 'dawnforge SAY_COMMANDER_DAWNFORGE_2'),
