	(21504, 4, 0, 'For the time being, yes.  However, allow my presence to be a motivator.  Prince Kael\'thas was displeased with the failure of the crystal experiment on Fallen Sky Ridge.  This is one of the reasons for why we chose the Cenarion druids as the testing grounds for the bomb.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 19162, 0, 'Pathaleon the Calculators Image'),
