	(24664, 0, 0, 'Don\'t look so smug! I know what you\'re thinking, but Tempest Keep was merely a setback. Did you honestly believe I would trust the future to some blind, half-night elf mongrel?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12413, 0, 25386, 0, 'Kael\'thas Sunstrider - Intro 1'),
