	(25162, 3, 0, 'First though, you sin\'dorei listen up. I run a tight ship... this isn\'t going to be like what you\'re used to with the Scryers. Pull your weight, or get back on the boat!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 24212, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum'),
	(25162, 4, 0, 'Now that that\'s out of the way, welcome to the Isle of Quel\'Danas. The Sunwell\'s on the plateau to the south, and Prince Kael\'thas is holed up in the Magisters\' Terrace to the east.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 24213, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum'),
	(25162, 5, 0, 'We\'re here as support for the so-called \'adventurers\' that the brass has called in. We\'ll help them hold the key points on the island, and keep the heat off so that they can do their jobs.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 24214, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum'),
	(25162, 6, 0, 'If none of you ladies have any questions, you can get further instructions and assignments from your squad leaders. That\'s it. Good luck!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 24215, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum'),
	(25162, 7, 0, 'Attention!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26245, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum'),
