	(27373, 1, 0, 'You know their kind as old gods.  Beware Yogg-Saron, the beast with a thousand maws.  His evil extends beyond Vordrassil\'s roots.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26437, 0, 'Spirit of Ursoc'),
	(27376, 0, 0, 'What do you mean my time has come?! I\'ll kill you where you stand!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26449, 0, 'Deathguard Schneider before going hostile'),
	(27376, 1, 0, 'Hey, over here!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 53162, 0, 'Deathguard Schneider upon LoS'),
	(27378, 0, 0, 'You can\'t possibly mean to.... I\'ll write you up for this, $c!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26450, 0, 'Senior Scrivener Barriga before going hostile'),
	(27378, 1, 0, 'If you\'d be so kind, please let me out of here!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26452, 0, 'Senior Scrivener Barriga upon LoS'),
	(27379, 0, 0, 'No! I beg you! Please don\'t kill me!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26454, 0, 'Engineer Burke before going hostile'),
	(27379, 1, 0, 'Can someone let me out of here? I need to get back to Venomspite and finish my shift.', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26453, 0, 'Engineer Burke upon LoS'),
	(27381, 0, 0, 'What is the meaning of this?! Stop! I\'ll double whatever they\'re paying you!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26458, 0, 'Chancellor Amai before going hostile'),
	(27381, 1, 0, 'I just arrived in Venomspite. How could I have possibly wronged you?', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26459, 0, 'Chancellor Amai upon Los'),
	(27383, 0, 0, 'I was... once like you. Mortal. Soft. Only flesh and bone. WEAK AND TIMID!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27157, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 1, 0, 'Our lord, Arthas saw in me the frailty of man.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27159, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 2, 0, '"Serve me in life and I will promise to rend the weakness from your soul. To erase it from existence!" To be chosen... blessed by the Lich King in such a way.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27160, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 3, 0, 'So serve him I did... Were it not for me the glorious dread citadel of Naxxramas may never have returned to Northrend.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27161, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 4, 0, 'But enough talk... You have fought hard and come from the distant reaches of this world to face the Duskbringer. I shall not disappoint...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27162, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 5, 0, 'Just as our lord saved me, so too shall I save you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27163, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 6, 0, 'THIS WILL BE THE LAST TIME YOU UTTER THAT NAME, PALADIN! Breathe your dying breath!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27176, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27383, 7, 0, 'Rise, my minions! Your master commands it!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27164, 0, 'Thel zan the Duskbringer'),
	(27389, 0, 0, 'By all means, don\'t assess the situation, you halfwit! Just jump into the fray!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13199, 0, 29527, 0, 'dalronn YELL_DALRONN_AGGRO'),
