	(27447, 3, 3, 'They are... too strong! Underestimated their... fortitude.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 13655, 0, 31819, 0, ''),
	(27447, 4, 0, 'Intruders, your victory will be short-lived. I am Commander Varos Cloudstrider. My drakes control the skies and protect this conduit. I will see to it personally that the Oculus does not fall into your hands!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13648, 0, 31812, 3, 'Varos Cloudstrider SAY_VAROS_INTRO_TEXT'),
	(27455, 0, 0, 'Captain, why are the guards not at their posts?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 12725, 0, 26714, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 1, 0, 'Uther had my troops recalled? Damn it! If my warriors abandon me, I\'ll never defeat Mal\'Ganis. The ships must be burned before the men reach the shore!\n', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 12726, 0, 26716, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 2, 0, 'Burned down to their frames! No one goes home until our job here is done!\n', 12, 0, 100, 15, 0, 12727, 0, 26718, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 3, 0, 'Spare me, Muradin. You weren\'t there to see what Mal\'Ganis did to my homeland.\n', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 12728, 0, 26732, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 4, 0, 'Behold, Muradin, our salvation, Frostmourne.\n', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 12729, 0, 27207, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 5, 0, 'I would gladly bear any curse to save my homeland.\n', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 12730, 0, 27211, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 6, 0, 'Damn the men! Nothing shall prevent me from having my revenge, old friend. Not even you.\n', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 12731, 0, 27214, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27455, 7, 0, 'Now, I call out to the spirits of this place. I will give anything or pay any price, if only you will help me save my people.\n', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 12732, 0, 27215, 0, 'Prince Arthas'),
	(27463, 0, 0, 'Ahh.... better.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26657, 0, 'wounded skirmisher RANDOM_SAY_1'),
	(27463, 0, 1, 'Whoa - I nearly died there. Thank you, $r!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26659, 0, 'wounded skirmisher RANDOM_SAY_2'),
	(27463, 0, 2, 'Thank you, $c.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26656, 0, 'wounded skirmisher RANDOM_SAY_3'),
	(27476, 0, 0, 'I apologize, emissary, but the prince is away on an errand. Wha brings you to this desolate place?', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3000, 12719, 0, 26709, 0, 'Valonforth 0  - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27476, 1, 0, 'We\'re to just pick up and leave?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 1500, 12720, 0, 26711, 0, 'Valonforth 1  - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27476, 2, 0, 'To hell with the undead! We\'ll cut our way through the woods, men!', 12, 0, 100, 22, 3000, 12721, 0, 26713, 0, 'Valonforth 2  - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27476, 3, 0, 'Well, milord, your father had our troops recalled at Lord Uther\'s request.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3000, 12722, 0, 26715, 0, 'Valonforth 3 - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27480, 0, 0, 'Isn\'t that a bit much, lad?\n', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 12733, 0, 26717, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27480, 1, 0, 'You lied to your men and betrayed the mercenaries who fought for you. What\'s happening to you, Arthas? Is vengeance all that\'s important to you?\n', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 12734, 0, 26731, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27480, 2, 0, 'Hold, lad. There\'s an inscription on the dais. It\'s a warning. It says, "Whomsoever takes up this blade shall wield power eternal. Just as the blade rends flesh, so must power scar the spirit." Oh, I should\'ve known. The blade is cursed! Let\'s get the hell out of here!\n', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12735, 0, 27209, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27480, 3, 0, 'Leave it be, Arthas. Forget this business and lead your men home.\n', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 12736, 0, 27212, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27480, 4, 0, 'O\' my head... Wh... Where am I?\n', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27217, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27480, 5, 0, 'Who... Who am I?\n', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27218, 0, 'Muradin'),
	(27482, 0, 0, 'I\'d nearly given up. You\'ve given me new life!', 12, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26684, 0, 'Wounded Westfall Infantry say text'),
	(27482, 0, 1, 'Bless you, friend. I nearly expired....', 12, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26682, 0, 'Wounded Westfall Infantry say text'),
	(27482, 0, 2, 'Without your help, I surely would have died....', 12, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26685, 0, 'Wounded Westfall Infantry say text'),
	(27482, 0, 3, 'Thank you, $r!', 12, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26683, 0, 'Wounded Westfall Infantry say text'),
	(27492, 0, 0, 'By royal edict, you men are to return to Lordaeron immediately. Lord Uther has convinced the king to recall this expedition.', 12, 0, 100, 25, 3500, 12723, 0, 26710, 0, 'Alliance Emissary 0 - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27492, 1, 0, 'That\'s correct. My men report that the roads from here to the shore are held by the undead. You\'ll need to find an alternate route back to your ships.', 12, 0, 100, 378, 4000, 12724, 0, 26712, 0, 'Alliance Emissary 1 - Q: The Truth Shall Set Us Free'),
	(27551, 0, 0, '%s goes into a frenzy!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 38630, 0, 'Enraged Apparition'),
	(27570, 0, 0, 'We\'re all gonna die!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26848, 0, 'venture co straggler SAY1'),
	(27570, 0, 1, 'Gotta get out of here!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26847, 0, 'venture co straggler SAY2'),
	(27570, 0, 2, 'No way I\'m stickin\' around!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26851, 0, 'venture co straggler SAY3'),
	(27570, 0, 3, 'Forget this! I\'m going home!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26850, 0, 'venture co straggler SAY4'),
	(27570, 0, 4, 'I didn\'t sign up for this!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26849, 0, 'venture co straggler SAY5'),
	(27577, 0, 0, '%s growls.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 409, 0, 26802, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 1, 0, '%s hisses!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 410, 0, 26805, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 2, 0, 'Tell you nothing, preacher.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26806, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 3, 0, 'What can you do to me that Kel\'Thuzad has not? That the Lich King will not?', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26807, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 4, 0, 'The book is your salvation, yes... but nothing will you know! NOTHING I SAY! NOTHING! ', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26808, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 5, 0, 'No more LIGHT! NO MORE! I BEG YOU!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26822, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 6, 0, 'Never felt hurt like this!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26823, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 7, 0, 'It tells of the coming apocalypse. How this world will burn and be reborn from death.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26825, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 8, 0, 'NOOOO!!! I tell you! I tell you everything!', 12, 0, 100, 39, 0, 0, 0, 26827, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 9, 0, 'Humans... Beneath the earth of Wintergarde Village you built a mausoleum! Why do you think Naxxramas attacked that spot? Thel\'zan hides deep in your own crypt and sends a thousand-thousand corpses at you! Perish you will...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26828, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 10, 0, 'How? Humans truly are stupid, yes? Thel\'zan the Duskbringer! Thel\'zan the Lich! He who is born of human flesh and bone, sacrificed all for power, protected by the Lich King!', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26831, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27577, 11, 0, 'You cannot stop Thel\'zan! He bears the dark gift, bestowed upon him by the Lich King himself!', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 26832, 0, 'Mayor Godfrey'),
	(27588, 0, 0, 'Without you we\'d be lost. Thanks for the ride!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26844, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 0, 1, 'For the Alliance and Lord Fordragon!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26841, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 0, 2, 'HOO-WAH! The cavalry has arrived!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26842, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 0, 3, 'Great driving, soldier! Not a scratch on us!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26843, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 0, 'I think I see one of their plague wagons!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26971, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 1, 'Did I ever tell you soldiers about the time I destroyed the Thandol Span? Yep, weren\'t no dark irons destroyed that bridge! Was me!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26972, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 2, 'It doesn\'t make any sense. Why don\'t they just fly Naxxramas over Wintergarde Keep and blow it up? I mean, that\'s what I would do if I were Kel\'Thuzad.', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26973, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 3, 'I wonder if we\'ll ever solve the mystery of the strange ore. There\'s gotta be some use for it!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26974, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 4, 'Hey, do any of you know McGoyver over at Valgarde? He\'s my uncle. You know what his title is? Pro. Yea, just "Pro." I want to be a pro too.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26975, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 5, 'Something straight up stinks in here! It\'s definitely not me. Gnomes smell like butter and sunshine. Not like those dwarves that smell like they were born from a trogg\'s armpit! None of you are dwarves, are you?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26976, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 6, 'I used to know a dwarf that claimed gnomes evolved from beneath the earth. That we all started out as sand gnomes. What a load of nonsense! Sand gnomes? PUH-LEASE!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26977, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 7, 'I\'ve never seen destruction like this...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26978, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 8, 'Keep the chatter down, people. We need to stay alert!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26979, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 9, 'The smell of death covers every inch of this place.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26980, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 10, 'Driver, I hear you single handedly airlifted our villagers out of this hell-hole. Is that true?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26981, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 11, 'So does anyone know anything about Thel\'zan? Who is he? How did he come to leading the Scourge armies on the ground?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26982, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 12, 'Look at this mess... The Scourge will pay for this!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26983, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 13, 'Where are all the corpses? What have they done to our people?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26984, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 1, 14, 'I hope I\'m alive to see Arthas get what\'s coming to him.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26985, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27588, 2, 0, 'Reporting for duty, sir!', 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26954, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27619, 0, 0, 'Rise, Arugal!  The power of the Lich King commands you!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26865, 0, 'Prince Valanar - Silverpine'),
	(27624, 0, 0, 'Yes... he shall suit our needs perfectly.  Have him sent to Solstice Village when you\'re ready.  Arthas will not be pleased if we fall behind schedule.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26867, 0, 'Prince Theraldis - Silverpine'),
	(27629, 0, 0, 'Are you ready for battle, $c?', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29966, 0, 'Wyrmrest Defender'),
