	(27654, 0, 0, 'The prisoners shall not go free! The word of Malygos is law!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13594, 0, 31793, 0, 'drakos SAY_AGGRO'),
	(27654, 1, 0, 'A fitting punishment.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13602, 0, 31801, 0, 'drakos SAY_KILL_1'),
	(27654, 1, 1, 'Sentence executed!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13603, 0, 31802, 0, 'drakos SAY_KILL_2'),
	(27654, 1, 2, 'Another casualty of war!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13604, 0, 31803, 0, 'drakos SAY_KILL_3'),
	(27654, 2, 0, 'The war... goes on.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13605, 0, 31804, 0, 'drakos SAY_DEATH'),
	(27654, 3, 0, 'It is too late to run!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13598, 0, 31797, 0, 'drakos SAY_PULL_1'),
	(27654, 3, 1, 'Gather \'round....', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13599, 0, 31798, 0, 'drakos SAY_PULL_2'),
	(27654, 3, 2, 'None shall escape!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13600, 0, 31799, 0, 'drakos SAY_PULL_3'),
	(27654, 3, 3, 'I condemn you to death!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13601, 0, 31800, 0, 'drakos SAY_PULL_4'),
	(27654, 4, 0, 'Tremble, worms!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13595, 0, 31794, 0, 'drakos SAY_STOMP_1'),
	(27654, 4, 1, 'I will crush you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13596, 0, 31795, 0, 'drakos SAY_STOMP_2'),
	(27654, 4, 2, 'Can you fly?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13597, 0, 31796, 0, 'drakos SAY_STOMP_3'),
	(27655, 0, 0, 'What do we have here... those that would defy the Spell-Weaver? Those without foresight or understanding. How can I make you see? Malygos is saving the world from itself! Bah! You are hardly worth my time!', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 13635, 0, 27411, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_SUMMON_1'),
	(27655, 1, 0, 'Clearly my pets failed. Perhaps another demonstration is in order.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 13636, 0, 27413, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_SUMMON_2'),
	(27655, 2, 0, 'Still you fight. Still you cling to misguided principles. If you survive, you\'ll find me in the center ring.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 13637, 0, 27414, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_SUMMON_3'),
	(27655, 3, 0, 'Poor blind fools!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13638, 0, 27412, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_AGGRO'),
	(27655, 4, 0, '%s begins to cast Empowered Arcane Explosion!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27903, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - EMOTE_ARCANE_EXPLOSION'),
	(27655, 5, 0, 'A taste... just a small taste... of the Spell-Weaver\'s power!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13639, 0, 31829, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_ARCANE_EXPLOSION'),
	(27655, 5, 1, 'So much unstable energy... but worth the risk to destroy you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13640, 0, 31830, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_ARCANE_EXPLOSION'),
	(27655, 6, 0, 'Everything I have done... has been for Azeroth....', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13644, 0, 31834, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_DEATH'),
	(27655, 7, 0, 'If only you understood!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13641, 0, 31831, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_PLAYER_KILL'),
	(27655, 7, 1, 'Now do you see? Do you?!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13642, 0, 31832, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_PLAYER_KILL'),
	(27655, 7, 2, 'Unfortunate, but necessary.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13643, 0, 31833, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom - SAY_PLAYER_KILL'),
	(27656, 0, 0, 'Simpletons! You cannot comprehend the forces you have set in motion. The ley line conduit will not be disrupted! Your defeat shall be absolute!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13622, 0, 31841, 3, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_SPAWN'),
	(27656, 1, 0, 'You brash interlopers are out of your element! I will ground you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13623, 0, 31873, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_AGGRO'),
	(27656, 2, 0, 'Such insolence... such arrogance... must be PUNISHED!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13624, 0, 31874, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_ENRAGE'),
	(27656, 3, 0, 'It\'s a long way down....', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13628, 0, 31878, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_KILL'),
	(27656, 3, 1, 'BACK to the earth with you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13629, 0, 31879, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_KILL'),
	(27656, 3, 2, 'Enjoy the fall!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13630, 0, 31880, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_KILL'),
	(27656, 4, 0, 'Savor this small victory, foolish little creatures. You and your dragon allies have won this battle, but we will win... the Nexus War.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13631, 0, 31881, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_DEATH'),
	(27656, 5, 0, 'We command the arcane! It shall not be used against us!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13626, 0, 31876, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_SHIELD'),
	(27656, 5, 1, 'It is trivial to extinguish your fire!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13627, 0, 31877, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_SHIELD'),
	(27656, 5, 2, 'No magic of nature will help you now!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13625, 0, 31875, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos - SAY_SHIELD'),
	(27658, 0, 0, 'Thank you for freeing us, mortals.  Beware, the blue flight is alerted to your presence.  Even now, Malygos sends Varos Cloudstrider and his ring guardians to defend the Oculus.  You will need our help to stand a chance.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3500, 0, 0, 26937, 0, 'Belgaristrasz - On freed'),
	(27683, 0, 0, 'I\'ve lived here and kept this shrine with the blessing of the Alexstrasza for longer than I can remember.  In its darkest hour, I\'ve failed... I fell at the feet of that damned death knight...  Bloodbane.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26939, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27683, 1, 0, 'Dahlia spits on the ground at the thought of the name.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26943, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27683, 2, 0, 'The Lich King is stretching his hand far now... fearlessly treading on the most sacred lands of all of the flights.  He intends to force us to action.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26940, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27683, 3, 0, 'My time is done... I offered myself to Alexstrasza in life, but I have nothing left to offer in death.  She will need a new keeper for her shrine.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26941, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27683, 4, 0, 'And thank you... thank you for freeing me from the shackles of the damned.  You are a hero... I know you will go on to great deeds.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26942, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27683, 5, 0, 'The Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch fades away...', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 26944, 0, 'Remnant of Dahlia Suntouch'),
	(27692, 0, 0, '%s flies away.', 16, 0, 100, 1, 0, 2858, 0, 25992, 0, 'Emerald - On take off'),
	(27692, 1, 0, 'Welcome Friend.  Keep your head down and hold on tight!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28136, 0, 'Emerald - On welcome'),
	(27692, 2, 0, 'Use Leeching Poison to damage enemies and keep me healed.  Touch the Nightmare is very powerful, but it hurts me, so only use it when I have a lot of health!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28255, 0, 'Emerald - On explaining abilities'),
	(27692, 3, 0, 'Now that I am at my full power I can perform Dream Funnel.  You can use it to heal other drakes, but it drains my health, so make sure you\'re using Leeching Poison too!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28259, 0, 'Emerald - On ultimate ability unlocked'),
	(27692, 4, 0, 'I\'m badly injured!  I can\'t take much more of this!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28257, 0, 'Emerald - On below 40%'),
	(27692, 5, 0, '$3486W Centrifuge Constructs remain.  We must find and destroy them to disable Varos Cloudstrider\'s protective shield.  The constructs should be about halfway up The Oculus, on the Band of Acceleration.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29518, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps 10 constructs'),
	(27692, 6, 0, 'One Centrifuge Construct remains.  We must find and destroy it to disable Varos Cloudstrider\'s protective shield.  The construct should be about halfway up The Oculus, on the Band of Acceleration.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29519, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps 1 construct'),
	(27692, 7, 0, 'The shield is down; Varos is vulnerable!  Defeating him should disperse the Azure Ring Guardians and allow us access to the upper bands.  Varos is on a floating platform about halfway up The Oculus, on the Band of Acceleration.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29520, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps Varos'),
	(27692, 8, 0, 'Mage-Lord Urom is our next target.  He should be hiding on one of the floating platforms on the Band of Transmutation, near the top of The Oculus.  Be warned, Urom is a powerful conjurer; he may not be alone.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29521, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps Lord Urom'),
	(27692, 9, 0, 'Ley-Guardian Eregos is all that now stands between us and control of The Oculus.  He\'s flying above the Band of Alignment, at the very top of The Oculus.  Eregos is incredibly powerful; stay on my back when we engage him and leave the fighting to me.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29522, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps Eregos'),
	(27692, 10, 0, 'We\'ve wrested control of The Oculus from the forces of Malygos.  You\'re not getting any lighter, little one.  My wings itch for the open sky.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Emerald - Say gps End'),
	(27713, 0, 0, 'What is it?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27143, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 1, 'Is this the end? If we stop this bastard now, is victory assured at the Wrathgate?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27146, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 2, 'Let it be known that it has been an honor and a privilege fighting alongside all of you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27148, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 3, 'Death comes for us all eventually, but sometimes it comes a little faster than anticipated. Today we call that blind heroics... Tomorrow someone may call it stupidity.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27150, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 4, 'Come on... Let\'s get this over with!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27149, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 5, 'It looks like a gateway to hell!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27144, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 6, 'I\'m getting a little worried. Where is this hero that is supposed to lead us into battle?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27147, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 0, 7, 'If I don\'t make it back to Wintergarde, let my family know that I did my best and that I love them...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27145, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27713, 1, 0, 'It\'s the Highlord!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27178, 0, '7th Legion Elite'),
	(27719, 0, 0, 'Ladies and gentlemen!  Well... let\'s just say you don\'t want to miss this one!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27032, 0, 'Grennix Shivwiggle - Quest Accepted'),
	(27726, 0, 0, 'I used good judgment when you showed none.  I don\'t want to see you lead us into ruin, Krenna!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27027, 0, 'Gorgonna - Say 0'),
	(27726, 1, 1, 'It doesn\'t have to end this way, you know?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27026, 0, 'Gorgonna - Say 1'),
	(27726, 2, 2, 'We\'ll see about that.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27028, 0, 'Gorgonna - Say 2'),
	(27726, 3, 3, 'Why... why sister?  Why did it have to come to this?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27033, 0, 'Gorgonna - Say 3'),
	(27727, 0, 0, 'You went behind my back.  You neglected my orders.  You will pay the price.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27030, 0, 'Conqueror Krenna - Say 0'),
	(27727, 1, 1, 'Enough talk.  By the time I\'m through with you, not even the worgs are going to want to go near your corpse.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 27031, 0, 'Conqueror Krenna - Say 1'),
	(27755, 0, 0, '%s flies away.', 16, 0, 100, 1, 0, 2858, 0, 25992, 0, 'Amber - On take off'),
	(27755, 1, 0, 'Welcome Friend.  Keep your head down and hold on tight!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28136, 0, 'Amber - On welcome'),
	(27755, 2, 0, 'Use Shock Lance to damage enemies.  If we get in trouble, Stop Time to freeze all enemies in place, then hit them with Shock Lance for massive damage!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28256, 0, 'Amber - On explaining abilities'),
