	(27756, 2, 0, 'Use Searing Wrath to damage enemies and Evasive Maneuvers if I start taking damage.  Remember I need to build up Evasive Charges by taking damage to perform Evasive Maneuvers!', 15, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 28254, 0, 'Ruby - On explaining abilities'),
