	(28610, 0, 5, 'I\'ll tear the secrets from your soul! Tell me about the "Crimson Dawn" and your life may be spared!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29138, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 0, 6, 'Is your life worth so little? Just tell me what I need to know about "Crimson Dawn" and I\'ll end your suffering quickly.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29139, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 0, 7, 'I grow tired of these games, human. Tell me of the "Crimson Dawn" or I will tear your spine out with my bare hands!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29140, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 0, 'I\'ll tell you nothing, Scourge filth!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29141, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 1, 'You\'\'ll have to kill me, monster. I will tell you NOTHING!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29142, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 2, 'Argh... The pain... The pain is almost as unbearable as the lashings I received in grammar school when I was but a child.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29143, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 3, 'You... You\'ll get nothing... And like it...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29144, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 4, 'Do you think this to be pain? To be suffering? HAH! Destroy this mortal shell so that I may ascend to the heavens!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29145, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 5, 'You hit like a girl. Honestly. Is that the best you can do?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29146, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
	(28610, 1, 6, 'The crimson what? Never heard of it...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29147, 0, 'Scarlet Marksman'),
