	(28948, 0, 0, 'Ahh... there you are. The master told us you\'d be arriving soon.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29127, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 1, 0, 'Please, follow me, $n. There is much for you to see....', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29128, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 2, 0, 'Ever since his arrival from Drak\'Tharon, the master has spoken of the time you would be joining him here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29172, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 3, 0, 'You should feel honored. You are the first of the master\'s prospects to be shown our operation.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29171, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 4, 0, 'The things I show you now must never be spoken of outside Voltarus. The world shall come to know our secret soon enough!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29173, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 5, 0, 'Here lie our stores of blight crystal, without which our project would be impossible.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29174, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 6, 0, 'I understand that you are to thank for the bulk of our supply.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29175, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 7, 0, 'These trolls are among those you exposed on the battlefield. Masterfully done, indeed....', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29176, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 8, 0, 'We feel it best to position them here, where they might come to terms with their impending fate.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29433, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 9, 0, 'This is their destiny....', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29434, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 10, 0, 'The blight slowly seeps into their bodies, gradually preparing them for their conversion.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29435, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 11, 0, 'This special preparation grants them unique powers far greater than they would otherwise know.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29436, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 12, 0, 'Soon, the master will grant them the dark gift, making them fit to serve the Lich King for eternity!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29437, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 13, 0, 'Stay for as long as you like, $n. Glory in the fruits of your labor!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29438, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
	(28948, 14, 0, 'Your service has been invaluable in fulfilling the master\'s plan. May you forever grow in power....', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29439, 0, 'Malmortis say'),
