	(29579, 0, 0, 'I... I can understand you now! Well, now that we can talk to each other, you have some explaining to do!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 30624, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text0'),
	(29579, 1, 0, 'How did you get my communicator from the Explorers\' League?', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 30625, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text1'),
	(29579, 2, 0, 'If the Explorers\' League sent men, I didn\'t see any trace of them. I found your note buried in a camp overrun by iron dwarves.', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30622, 0, 'Player text2'),
	(29579, 3, 0, 'You have my thanks for dispatching the iron dwarves. But why would the Horde have an interest in me?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 30626, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text3'),
	(29579, 4, 0, 'A scout found the remains of your journal in Thor Modan. We\'ve been looking for you ever since.', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30623, 0, 'Player text4'),
	(29579, 5, 0, 'That wouldn\'t be Scout Vor\'takh, would it? Even I know of his reputation for ruthlessness. He means to abduct me, then?', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 30627, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text5'),
	(29579, 6, 0, 'If you\'ve seen the journal, then you know what I\'ve been discovering. The titans\' own creations are at war with each other!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 30628, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text6'),
	(29579, 7, 0, 'Loken and his iron dwarf minions have ousted the Earthen from Ulduar and taken over the city.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 30629, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text7'),
	(29579, 8, 0, 'If we spend our time and strength fighting with each other, Loken will use Ulduar\'s resources to destroy both Horde and Alliance.', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 30630, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard text8'),
	(29579, 9, 0, 'Speak to the commander at your post, $g lad:lass;, and persuade him to abandon Vor\'takh\'s foolish plan.', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 30631, 0, 'Brann Bronzebeard Text10'),
	(29614, 0, 0, 'Even in death there will be no escape for you!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30267, 0, 'Onslaught Darkweaver'),
	(29614, 0, 1, 'I shall feast upon your soul!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30268, 0, 'Onslaught Darkweaver'),
	(29614, 0, 2, 'Now you know. Now you must die!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30266, 0, 'Onslaught Darkweaver'),
