	(34996, 12, 0, 'A shallow and tragic victory. We are weaker as a whole from the losses suffered today. Who but the Lich King could benefit from such foolishness? Great warriors have lost their lives. And for what? The true threat looms ahead - the Lich King awaits us all in death.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16049, 0, 35721, 0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - Faction Champions Outro'),
