	(36954, 0, 0, 'Your allies have arrived, Jaina, just as you promised. You will all become powerful agents of the Scourge..', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17212, 0, 37172, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LICH_KING_AGGRO_A'),
