	(36955, 8, 0, 'Forgive me, heroes. I should have listened to Uther. I... I just had to see for myself. To look into his eyes one last time. I am sorry.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16648, 0, 36990, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_FINAL_2'),
	(36955, 9, 0, 'We now know what must be done. I will deliver this news to King Varian and Highlord Fordring.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16649, 0, 36991, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_FINAL_3'),
	(36990, 0, 0, 'Why should the Banshee Queen spare your miserable life?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17033, 0, 36845, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_2'),
	(36990, 1, 0, 'Frostmourne? The Lich King is never without his blade. If you are lying to me...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17034, 0, 36846, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_4'),
	(36990, 2, 0, 'A fitting end for a traitor. Come, we must free the slaves and see what is within the Lich King\'s chamber for ourselves.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17035, 0, 36847, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_10'),
	(36990, 3, 0, 'Take cover behind me! Quickly!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17037, 0, 37540, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_3'),
	(36990, 4, 0, 'I thought he\'d never shut up. At last, Sindragosa silenced that long-winded fool. To the Halls of Reflection, champions! Our objective is near... I can sense it.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17036, 0, 37541, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_4'),
