	(37129, 6, 0, 'Augh! I must rest for a moment. \n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16826, 0, 37164, 0, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_GAUNTLET'),
	(37129, 7, 0, 'Champions! I cannot hold her back any longer.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16827, 0, 37165, 0, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_SVALNA'),
	(37129, 8, 0, 'Vengeance alone... was not enough!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16828, 0, 0, 0, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_DEATH'),
	(37157, 0, 0, 'Guards!I expect this $r to be clapped into chains!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36947, 0, 'on Aggro Text'),
	(37158, 0, 0, '%s prepares to attack!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37211, 0, 'Quel\'Delar'),
	(37171, 0, 0, '%s becomes enraged!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 10677, 0, 'combat Enrage'),
	(37172, 0, 0, 'You know, that does smell pretty... Hey! Stop spraying that thing at me!', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 38296, 0, 'Detective Snap Snagglebolt'),
	(37172, 1, 0, 'Don\'t tempt me! Do you even know what\'s in those things?', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 38382, 0, 'Detective Snap Snagglebolt'),
	(37173, 0, 0, 'What we gon\' do now, you ask?  We wait.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36957, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari'),
	(37173, 1, 0, 'Grik\'nir says he gon\' talk to the elemental, get it to fight on our side.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36960, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari'),
	(37173, 2, 0, 'Soon enough we take over dis valley.  Soon enough.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36961, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari'),
	(37174, 0, 0, 'Our land be a land of ice an\' snow.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36963, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa'),
	(37174, 1, 0, 'But beneath the earth, child, there always be fire.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36964, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa'),
	(37174, 2, 0, 'De spirit come from deep down to talk with Grik\'nir.', 12, 0, 100, 396, 0, 0, 0, 36965, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa'),
	(37181, 0, 0, 'You now stand upon the hallowed ground of the Scourge. The Light won\'t protect you here, paladin. Nothing will protect you...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17230, 0, 38054, 0, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_1'),
	(37181, 1, 0, 'You could have been my greatest champion, Fordring: A force of darkness that would wash over this world and deliver it into a new age of strife.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17231, 0, 38055, 0, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_2'),
	(37181, 2, 0, 'But that honor is no longer yours. Soon, I will have a new champion. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17232, 0, 38056, 0, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_3'),
	(37181, 3, 0, 'The breaking of this one has been taxing. The atrocities I have committed upon his soul. He has resisted for so long, but he will bow down before his king soon.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17233, 0, 37034, 0, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_4'),
	(37181, 4, 0, 'In the end, you will all serve me.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17234, 0, 38059, 0, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_5'),
	(37183, 0, 0, 'NEVER! I... I will never... serve... you...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17078, 0, 37035, 0, 'Highlord Bolvar Fordragon - SAY_BOLVAR_INTRO_1'),
	(37184, 0, 0, 'Rocket Pack Active!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37537, 0, 'Zafod Boombox - SAY_ZAFOD_ROCKET_PACK_ACTIVE'),
	(37184, 1, 0, 'Rocket Pack Disabled. Move closer to Zafod Boombox to re-activate.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37538, 0, 'Zafod Boombox - SAY_ZAFOD_ROCKET_PACK_DISABLED'),
	(37187, 0, 0, 'Kor\'kron, move out! Champions, watch your backs. The Scourge have been...', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 17103, 0, 37634, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_1'),
	(37187, 1, 0, 'My boy died at the Wrath Gate. I am here only to collect his body.', 12, 0, 0, 397, 0, 17097, 0, 37638, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_3'),
	(37187, 2, 0, 'We named him Dranosh - It means "Heart of Draenor" in orcish. I would not let the warlocks take him. My boy would be safe, hidden away by the elders of Garadar.', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 17098, 0, 37640, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_5'),
	(37187, 3, 0, 'I made a promise to his mother before she died; that I would cross the Dark Portal alone - whether I lived or died, my son would be safe. Untainted...', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 17099, 0, 37641, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_6'),
	(37187, 4, 0, 'Today, I fulfill that promise.', 12, 0, 0, 397, 0, 17100, 0, 37642, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_7'),
	(37187, 5, 0, '%s charges!', 16, 0, 0, 53, 0, 17104, 0, 37643, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_8'),
	(37187, 6, 0, 'Behind you lies the body of my only son. Nothing will keep me from him. ', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17094, 0, 37525, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_8'),
	(37187, 7, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang walks over to his son and kneels before his son\'s body.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_12'),
	(37187, 8, 0, '[Orcish] No\'ku kil zil\'nok ha tar.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17096, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_13'),
	(37187, 9, 0, 'Higher Overlord Saurfang picks up the body of his son and walks over towards Varian', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_14'),
	(37187, 10, 0, 'I will not forget this... kindness. I thank you, Highness', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17095, 0, 37529, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_15'),
	(37187, 11, 0, '%s coughs.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17105, 0, 37646, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_1'),
	(37187, 12, 0, '%s weeps over the corpse of his son.', 16, 0, 0, 15, 0, 17106, 0, 37647, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_2'),
	(37187, 13, 0, 'You will have a proper ceremony in Nagrand, next to the pyres of your mother and ancestors.\n', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17101, 0, 37648, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_3'),
	(37187, 14, 0, 'Honor, young heroes... no matter how dire the battle... never forsake it.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17102, 0, 37649, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_4'),
	(37187, 15, 0, 'The paladin still lives? Is it possible, Highlord? Could he have survived?', 12, 0, 0, 6, 0, 17107, 0, 37051, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_1'),
	(37187, 16, 0, 'Then we must save him! If we rescue Bolvar Fordragon, we may quell the unrest between the Alliance and the Horde.', 12, 0, 0, 5, 0, 17108, 0, 37053, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2'),
	(37187, 17, 0, 'Our mission is now clear: The Lich King will answer for his crimes and we will save Highlord Bolvar Fordragon!', 12, 0, 0, 15, 0, 17109, 0, 37054, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3'),
	(37187, 18, 0, 'Kor\'kron, prepare Orgrim\'s Hammer for its final voyage! Champions, our gunship will find a point to dock on the upper reaches of the citadel. Meet us there!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 17110, 0, 37055, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4'),
	(37188, 0, 0, '%s cries.', 16, 0, 0, 18, 0, 16651, 0, 29772, 0, 'Lady Jaina Proudmoore - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_17'),
	(37188, 1, 0, 'It was nothing, your majesty. Just... I\'m proud of my king.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16652, 0, 37546, 0, 'Lady Jaina Proudmoore - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_19'),
	(37195, 0, 0, 'Get our men in position immediately, Tobias.  We cannot let the Scythe fall into the hands of the Forsaken!!', 12, 0, 100, 53, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Lord Darius Crowley to Player'),
	(37195, 1, 0, 'Lorna!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19511, 0, 0, 0, 'Lord Darius Crowley to Player'),
	(37195, 2, 0, 'Does this toad speak for you, Genn?  Do you come to our dwelling as a friend?  Or do you come as a tyrant?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19510, 0, 0, 0, 'Lord Darius Crowley to Player'),
	(37195, 3, 0, 'Aye, Genn.  It is not law that binds us.  It is something far stronger.  My men are ready to give their lives under your command.', 12, 0, 100, 273, 0, 19512, 0, 0, 0, 'Lord Darius Crowley to Player'),
	(37200, 0, 0, 'Let\'s get a move on then! Move ou...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16974, 0, 37457, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_1'),
	(37200, 1, 0, 'A lone orc against the might of the Alliance???', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16970, 0, 37460, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_4'),
	(37200, 2, 0, 'Charge!!!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16971, 0, 37461, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_5'),
	(37200, 3, 0, '%s gasps for air.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16975, 0, 37502, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_1'),
	(37200, 4, 0, 'That was Saurfang\'s boy - the Horde commander at the Wrath Gate. Such a tragic end...', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16976, 0, 37503, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_2'),
	(37200, 5, 0, 'What in the... There, in the distance!\n', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16977, 0, 37504, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_3'),
	(37200, 6, 0, 'A Horde Zeppelin flies up to the rise.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_4'),
	(37200, 7, 0, 'Soldiers, fall in! Looks like the Horde are comin\' to take another shot!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16978, 0, 37505, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_5'),
	(37200, 8, 0, 'The Zeppelin docks, and High Overlord Saurfang hops out, confronting the Alliance soldiers and Muradin', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_6'),
	(37200, 9, 0, 'Don\'t force me hand, orc. We can\'t let ye pass.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16972, 0, 37524, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_7'),
	(37200, 10, 0, 'I... I can\'t do it. Get back on yer ship and we\'ll spare yer life. ', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16973, 0, 37526, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_9'),
	(37200, 11, 0, 'A mage portal from Stormwind appears between the two and Varian Wrynn and Jaina Proudmoore emerge.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_10'),
	(37200, 12, 0, 'Right away, yer majesty!', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16979, 0, 37547, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_21'),
	(37200, 13, 0, 'Could it be, Lord Fordring? If Bolvar lives, mayhap there is hope fer peace between the Alliance and the Horde. We must reach the top o\' this cursed place and free the paladin!', 12, 0, 0, 6, 0, 16980, 0, 37037, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2'),
	(37200, 14, 0, 'Prepare the Skybreaker fer an aerial assault on the citadel!', 14, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16981, 0, 37043, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3'),
	(37200, 15, 0, 'Heroes, ye must fight yer way to a clear extraction point within Icecrown. We\'ll try an\' rendezvous on the ramparts!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16982, 0, 37046, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4'),
	(37217, 0, 0, '%s cries out with a loud, baying howl!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37849, 0, 'Precious - EMOTE_PRECIOUS_ZOMBIES'),
	(37221, 0, 0, 'The chill of this place... I can feel my blood freezing.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16631, 0, 37591, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_1'),
	(37221, 1, 0, 'What is that! Up ahead! Could it be? Heroes, at my side!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16632, 0, 37592, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_2'),
	(37221, 2, 0, 'Frostmourne: the blade that destroyed our kingdom...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16633, 0, 37593, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_3'),
	(37221, 3, 0, 'Stand back! Touch that blade and your soul will be scarred for all eternity! I must attempt to commune with the spirits locked away within Frostmourne. Give me space. Back up, please. ', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16634, 0, 37594, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_4'),
	(37221, 4, 0, 'Uther! Dear Uther! I... I\'m so sorry.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16635, 0, 37595, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_5'),
	(37221, 5, 0, 'Arthas is here? Maybe I...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16636, 0, 37596, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_6'),
	(37221, 6, 0, 'But Uther, if there\'s any hope of reaching Arthas. I... I must try.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16637, 0, 37597, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_7'),
	(37221, 7, 0, 'Tell me how, Uther? How do I destroy my prince? My...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16638, 0, 37598, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_8'),
	(37221, 8, 0, 'You\'re right, Uther. Forgive me. I... I don\'t know what got a hold of me. We will deliver this information to the King and the knights that battle the Scourge within Icecrown Citadel.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16639, 0, 37599, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_9'),
	(37221, 9, 0, 'Who could bear such a burden?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16640, 0, 37600, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_10'),
	(37221, 10, 0, 'Then maybe there is still hope...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16641, 0, 37601, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_11'),
	(37221, 11, 0, 'You won\'t deny me this, Arthas! I must know... I must find out... ', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16642, 0, 37602, 0, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_END'),
	(37223, 0, 0, 'I... I don\'t believe it! Frostmourne stands before us - unguarded - just as the gnome claimed. Come, heroes!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17049, 0, 37568, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_1'),
	(37223, 1, 0, 'Standing this close to the blade that ended my life... The pain... It is renewed.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17050, 0, 37569, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_2'),
	(37223, 2, 0, 'I dare not touch it. Stand back! Stand back as I attempt to commune with the blade! Perhaps our salvation lies within...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17051, 0, 37570, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_3'),
	(37223, 3, 0, 'Uther... Uther the Lightbringer. How...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17052, 0, 37571, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_4'),
	(37223, 4, 0, 'The Lich King is here? Then my destiny shall be fulfilled on this day! ', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17053, 0, 37572, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_5'),
	(37223, 5, 0, 'There must be a way...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17054, 0, 37573, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_6'),
	(37223, 6, 0, 'Who could bear such a burden?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17055, 0, 37600, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_7'),
	(37223, 7, 0, 'The Frozen Throne...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17056, 0, 37575, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_8'),
	(37223, 8, 0, 'You will not escape me that easily, Arthas! I will have my vengeance! ', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17057, 0, 37576, 0, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_END'),
	(37225, 0, 0, 'Jaina! Could it truly be you?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16666, 0, 37603, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_1'),
	(37225, 1, 0, 'Jaina, you haven\'t much time. The Lich King sees what the sword sees. He will be here shortly. ', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16667, 0, 37604, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_2'),
	(37225, 2, 0, 'No, girl. Arthas is not here. Arthas is merely a presence within the Lich King\'s mind. A dwindling presence...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16668, 0, 37605, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_3'),
	(37225, 3, 0, 'Jaina, listen to me. You must destroy the Lich King. You cannot reason with him. He will kill you and your allies and raise you all as powerful soldiers of the Scourge.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16669, 0, 37606, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_4'),
	(37225, 4, 0, 'Snap out of it, girl. You must destroy the Lich King at the place where he merged with Ner\'zhul - atop the spire, at the Frozen Throne. It is the only way.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16670, 0, 37607, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_5'),
	(37225, 5, 0, 'There is... something else that you should know about the Lich King. Control over the Scourge must never be lost. Even if you were to strike down the Lich King, another would have to take his place. For without the control of its master, the Scourge would run rampant across the world - destroying all living things.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16671, 0, 37608, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_6'),
	(37225, 6, 0, 'A grand sacrifice by a noble soul...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16672, 0, 37609, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_7'),
	(37225, 7, 0, 'I do not know, Jaina. I suspect that the piece of Arthas that might be left inside the Lich King is all that holds the Scourge from annihilating Azeroth.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16673, 0, 37610, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_8'),
	(37225, 8, 0, 'No, Jaina! ARRRRRRGHHHH... He... He is coming. You... You must...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16674, 0, 37611, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_9'),
	(37225, 9, 0, 'Careful, girl. I\'ve heard talk of that cursed blade saving us before. Look around you and see what has been born of Frostmourne.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16659, 0, 37583, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_1'),
	(37225, 10, 0, 'You haven\'t much time. The Lich King sees what the sword sees. He will be here shortly. ', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16660, 0, 37584, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_2'),
	(37225, 11, 0, 'You cannot defeat the Lich King. Not here. You would be a fool to try. He will kill those that follow you and raise them as powerful soldiers of the Scourge. But for you, Sylvanas, his reward for you would be worse than the last.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16661, 0, 37585, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_3'),
	(37225, 12, 0, 'Perhaps, but know this: there must always be a Lich King. Even if you were to strike down Arthas, another would have to take his place, for without the control of the Lich King, the Scourge would wash over this world like locusts, destroying all that they touched.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16662, 0, 37586, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_4'),
	(37225, 13, 0, 'I do not know, Banshee Queen. I suspect that the piece of Arthas that might be left inside the Lich King is all that holds the Scourge from annihilating Azeroth.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16663, 0, 37587, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_5'),
	(37225, 14, 0, 'Alas, the only way to defeat the Lich King is to destroy him at the place where he was created.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16664, 0, 37588, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_6'),
	(37225, 15, 0, 'Aye. ARRRRRRGHHHH... He... He is coming. You... You must...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16665, 0, 37589, 0, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_H2_7'),
	(37225, 16, 0, 'Halt! Do not carry that blade any further!', 14, 0, 100, 25, 0, 16675, 0, 37201, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37225, 17, 0, 'Do you realize what you\'ve done?', 14, 0, 100, 5, 0, 16676, 0, 37202, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37225, 18, 0, 'You have forged this blade from saronite, the very blood of an old god. The power of the Lich King calls to this weapon.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16677, 0, 37204, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37225, 19, 0, 'Each moment you tarry here, Quel\'Delar drinks in the evil of this place.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16678, 0, 38442, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37225, 20, 0, 'There is only one way to cleanse this sword. Make haste for the Sunwell and immerse the blade in its waters.', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 16679, 0, 37205, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37225, 21, 0, 'I can resist Frostmourne\'s call no more...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16680, 0, 37206, 0, 'Uther the Lightbringer'),
	(37226, 0, 0, 'SILENCE, PALADIN!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17225, 0, 37613, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LK_INTRO_1'),
	(37226, 1, 0, 'So you wish to commune with the dead? You shall have your wish.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17226, 0, 37614, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LK_INTRO_2'),
	(37226, 2, 0, 'Falric. Marwyn. Bring their corpses to my chamber when you are through.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17227, 0, 37615, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LK_INTRO_3'),
	(37226, 3, 0, 'Foolish girl. You seek that which I killed long ago. He is merely a ghost now. A faint echo in my mind... ', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17229, 0, 37617, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LK_JAINA_INTRO_END'),
	(37226, 4, 0, 'I will not make the same mistake again, Sylvanas. This time there will be no escape. You will all serve me in death!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17228, 0, 37616, 0, 'Lich King SAY_LK_SYLVANAS_INTRO_END'),
	(37230, 0, 0, 'A screeching cry pierces the air above!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37161, 1, 'Spire Frostwyrm to Player'),
	(37491, 1, 0, 'You miserable fools never did manage to select a decent bat wing.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16587, 0, 37076, 0, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_RESURRECTED'),
	(37491, 2, 0, 'THAT was for bringing me spoiled spider ichor!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16588, 0, 37075, 0, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_KILL'),
	(37491, 3, 0, 'Don\'t... let Finklestein use me... for his potions...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16589, 0, 37077, 0, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SECOND_DEATH'),
	(37493, 1, 0, 'What? This strength...? All of the pain is gone! You... must join me in the eternal embrace of death!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16811, 0, 37664, 0, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_RESURRECTED'),
