	(37813, 0, 0, 'For every Horde soldier that you killed -- for every Alliance dog that fell, the Lich King\'s armies grew. Even now the val\'kyr work to raise your fallen as Scourge.\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16701, 0, 37458, 0, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_2'),
	(37813, 1, 0, 'Things are about to get much worse. Come, taste the power that the Lich King has bestowed upon me!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16702, 0, 37459, 0, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_3'),
