	(37846, 1, 0, 'Quel\'Delar.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16808, 0, 37484, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 1'),
	(37846, 2, 0, 'Quiet, fools. If I had wished to kill you, you\'d already be dead.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37894, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 2'),
	(37846, 3, 0, 'As Quel\'Serrar was forged by the dragons and given to the kaldorei, its twin, Quel\'Delar, was given to my people.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16809, 0, 37485, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 3'),
	(37846, 4, 0, 'The king bestowed the blade upon my friend, Thalorien Dawnseeker.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16800, 0, 37486, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 4'),
	(37846, 5, 0, 'But even Thalorien\'s skill and Quel\'Delar\'s magic could not save Silvermoon from the might of the Scourge.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16801, 0, 37487, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 5'),
	(37846, 6, 0, 'Thalorien fell before the gates of the Sunwell, buying time for others to escape.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16802, 0, 37488, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 6'),
	(37846, 7, 0, 'After the battle, I recovered the sword from the field. I bore it to Northrend in the service of my prince, seeking to avenge our people\'s defeat.', 12, 0, 100, 16, 0, 16803, 0, 37490, 0, 'Blood Queen Lana\'thel - Say 7'),
